Addon.name: Copper Golem Friend
Addon.role: This addon adds a copper golem, which was shown at Minecon 2021. Unfortunately, he can't press the buttons, but he will become a friend for you. Initially, he will be afraid of anything that can harm him. But if you tame him, he will be your protector and faithful companion.

Addon.role: Well Its quiet Easy to explain.This addon adds (13) New Golems into MC!These are quiet simple Golems but some have special abilitys and the better the Golem the Bigger :PSo welp Hope you enjoy! :)   Btw Turn on All experimental Gameplay Features  On

Addon.name: More Golems Remastered! (V2 Update!)
Addon.role: I've decide to remaster my old more golems addon. Have you ever wanted custom golems? Well your dreams has come true! This addon adds 10+ custom golems! Diamond Golem, Golden Golem, Emerald Golem, and much more!

Addon.name: Turtles Addon

Addon.role: This addon doubles the cuteness of axolotls by doubling the number of variants they have!

Addon.name: OceanCraft PE Addon
Addon.role: This add-on replaces some of the mobs in-game with the aquatic life. Some of the new creatures include sharks, whales, crabs and shrimps. Most of these won't spawn naturally in water though, so this means you will have to spawn them yourself using the various spawn eggs or by using text commands. Bring new life to the oceans with the OceanCraft PE Addon!
Addon.file_url: https://kossandroid.com/Data Android/Minecraft/Axolotls/9/OCEANCRAFT PE ADDON BY FERNAN.mcaddon

Addon.name: The Orca Addon
Addon.role: The Orca is an aggressive mob that replaces the dolphin. This is a mob that you definitely want to stay away from as it can deal 5 attack damage. The Orca can also sometimes dive onto the land where it can attack you if you are not careful! Since the orca is classed as a monster, the orca can also attack villagers. In total the orca has 200 health. I recommend that you fight more than one as the battle may become too easy. As a reward the orca can drop between 1-7 diamonds. Good Luck!

Addon.name: Biome: Project 0 Add-on (Support Update) (1.10.0.3+ beta)
Addon.role: The support update is finally here! As one of the first add-ons to implement new mobs to the game, this add-on now supports the newest beta versions, it includes fixes, adjustments, tweaks, and new functions.

Addon.name: Axolotl Concept Add-On
Addon.role: In this add-on, it adds a new little cute hostile mob that was shown at Minecraft Live 2020. Axolotl lives in Lush Caves in the next upcoming update 'Summer 2021', but for now, they will spawn in the tropical and oceans biomes.

Addon.name: Billey's Mobs Add-on
Addon.role: This is an add-on which implements 23(24 counting the wip goose) new mobs to the game. The mobs include everything from sea creatures such as the anglerfish and swordfish to pets which live on land such as the skeleton cat, the snail and the pigeon. It's a great addition to the game if you want to make aquariums with cool-looking fish or get awesome pets like a penguin that hunts fish for you or a skeleton cat that brings you items from the nether or even ride a special duck, make it change color and put a hat on it.

Addon.name: Minecraft But You Breathe Water (Updated) (Behavior)
Addon.role: In this add-on you will breathe water, so if you go out and breath air you will lose air bubbles, if you lose all your air bubbles you will lose hearths, if you lose all your hearths you will die, so... Can you survive?

Thats why I made this addon, that adds a lot of new behaviors for the Minecraft Dolphins. Even some really awesome animated tricks!

Addon.name: Seas and Oceans (by Asian Roofs Team)

Addon.name: Ex-Mermaids Add-On (1.17)
Addon.role: This Addon Add a new mob, a mermaid, this mermaid can be found commonly in the ocean, it can be tamed to go everywhere! and if you get tired of exploring by sea you can turn her into a human or other creatures!

Addon.name: Diving Tools Addon (1.16) (Gives Effect)
Addon.role: Hello there. Have you ever thought about bringing diving gear to Minecraft? Then this extension is for you! Thanks to this plug-in, you will have a much better view in the water and you will be able to breathe in the water. Also now gives conduit power effects when you wear all of the armor! Let's learn add-on better 😁

Addon.name: Shark Add-on
Addon.role: You wondered what sharks would be in minecraft? With this add-on you can get an idea of how a shark could be in minecraft! Sharks are very aggressive and attack any player that comes close!

Addon.name: Piranha Add-on
Addon.role: This add-on replaces the Salmon with deadly Piranhas which will attack their victim in groups. They are hostile by default and will always attack anyone who dare get near them. The core idea for this add-on was to make the sea slightly more dangerous. From here on, you will most likely be more careful next time you go for a swim!

Map.name: Aquatic Parkour [Parkour]
Map.role: Aquatic Parkour is a challenging parkour map consisting of 10 different parkour levels. Each level is based on something in Minecraft relating to the sea. This can be everything from a specific mob to an underwater structure. You can either play this map alone or together with other players. Your objective is to complete each level by jumping around on the different blocks and reaching the final platform. Step on the pressure plate to teleport to the next level.

Texture.name: Mob Hider V26 (New Mob Added!)

Texture.name: Hippocampus (Seahorse) Resource Pack
Texture.role: This resource pack adds a new aquatic fish to the game known as the Hippocampus (or more commonly seahorse). They exist as more than 3000 different color variations. You can either find them spawning naturally in your world in coral reefs or spawn them manually by spawning Tropical Fish. However, it doesn't seem to replace the Tropical Fish as they are still also possible to spawn. You can catch and carry them with a bucket. Creator: In Nova, Twitter Account

Texture.role: This addon contains a biome pack that generates a world of shallow seas and marshlands.  I made this one by accident and found that many of the ships were raised to the surface.  Most of the vanilla biomes are represented but flattened a bit or changed in strange ways.
